title: Sewing Garment Construction Fashion Design Patternmaking Megapac
description:
This is every book, magazine and article I could pull together on the subject of sewing. Everything from beginning to professional garment construction. I converted everything to PDF, OCR'd everything, and organized into folders to make it easier to identify what you want.
